{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div data-lake-element=\"root\" class=\"lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-parser-by=\"lake2html\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">除了默认的 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">docker0</code> 网桥，用户也可以指定网桥来连接各个容器。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">在启动 Docker 服务的时候，使用 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">-b BRIDGE</code>或<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">--bridge=BRIDGE</code> 来指定使用的网桥。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">如果服务已经运行，那需要先停止服务，并删除旧的网桥。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%228c5a2ac5%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20systemctl%20stop%20docker%5Cn%24%20sudo%20ip%20link%20set%20dev%20docker0%20down%5Cn%24%20sudo%20brctl%20delbr%20docker0%22%7D\" id=\"8c5a2ac5\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo systemctl stop docker\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo ip link set dev docker0 down\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ sudo brctl delbr docker0</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">然后创建一个网桥 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">bridge0</code>。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%220b857dd9%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20sudo%20brctl%20addbr%20bridge0%5Cn%24%20sudo%20ip%20addr%20add%20192.168.5.1%2F24%20dev%20bridge0%5Cn%24%20sudo%20ip%20link%20set%20dev%20bridge0%20up%22%7D\" id=\"0b857dd9\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(